response.original_title: Doraemon & F Character All StarsDream Town, F Land
response.overview: The "F Theater" on the second floor of the Kawasaki City Fujiko F Fujio Museum is screening short films that can only be seen here! Starting on Wednesday, February 21st, the latest work "Doraemon & F Character All-Stars Dream Town, F Land" will be released. This is an original short animated film for the museum, based on the story of the third volume of the Tentomushi Comics "Doraemon" "Dream Town, Nobita Land" and the 32nd volume "Anything Airport". This work is fitting for the 90th anniversary of the birth of Fujiko F Fujio, with a large gathering of F characters.
